<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Oerween" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">O'erween,</orth> to think arrogantly, to presume: <cit><quote>or I o. to think so,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.2.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 2, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a hot --ing cur,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.151" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 1, 151</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my heart --s too much,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.2.144" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 2, 144</bibl></cit>.
